.Dd June 24, 2026
.Dt X11DND_SOURCE_GET_DISPLAY 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm x11dnd_source_get_display
.Nd retrieve the Display from a drag source session
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libx11dnd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In x11dnd.h
.Ft Display *
.Fn x11dnd_source_get_display "X11DndSourceSession *sess"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn x11dnd_source_get_display
returns the
.Vt Display
that was passed to
.Xr x11dnd_start_drag 3
when the session was created.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The source
.Vt Display *
pointer.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr x11dnd_start_drag 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd_target_get_display 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd 3
